# Kusto Query Language

In this article:
1.	Overview
2.	Query Statements
3.	Management Commands
4.	KQL in other services 
5.	Related stuff 

## Overview

This article provides an explanation of the Kusto Query Language (KQL) and offers practical exercises to get you started writing queries. 
To access the query environment, use the Azure Data Explorer web UI. To learn how to use KQL, see Tutorial: Learn common operators.

